{
  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Fix Hero Headline Paragraph Visibility Issue\n\nImprove the contrast and readability of the paragraph text within the hero-headline section that is currently difficult to see due to insufficient contrast with the hero overlay shadow.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify the current paragraph text color in the hero-headline component\n- Analyze the hero overlay shadow color and opacity causing the contrast issue\n- Adjust the paragraph text color to ensure sufficient contrast ratio (minimum WCAG AA standard: 4.5:1 for normal text)\n- Consider alternative solutions: modify overlay opacity, add text shadow, or apply background gradient\n- Test visibility across different screen sizes and devices\n- Ensure the fix maintains the overall design aesthetic\n- Verify readability in various lighting conditions if possible",
